div.div: Students Enrolled By Year Per Course , Bar chart with 2 groups and 6 total bars. Use the arrow keys to navigate chart information and Tab to access the chart content.
X axis shows Year and has values 2020, and 2021.
Y axis shows Students and ranges from 0 to 70.
Legend shows Course and has values CS, Math, and Science.
